<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Well I cannot cast sow and I am quite glad I don't have to deal with beggers of this type.  But I totally agree that no one NEEDS sow.  If I ever want a sow I'll usually nicely role play the situation explaining why I need the sow.  And asking if I can get one when mana allows.  At the higher levels the mana is just about nothing but when you are talking about people under 20 it can really hurt them if they are trying to fight.  What bothers me is when I'm in a group pulling from somewhere and some guy is soling pulling the same mobs (which there aren't enough of) and he keeps coming asking for sow from a group member.  If he wants to fight there and share the spawns that's fine.  But when he can't do it without the help of our group he should either join us (so we share the xp) or get his own group.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
