<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I couldn't let all you barbarians have the only word.  Us Ogres have to WEIGH in here, too.  I must have been very fortunate.  I have had little contact with rude beggars.  I agree that they should be told "no" firmly.  I have filled many polite requests while I was medding, and then had those same people come to my aid later in my play when my back was to the wall.  I like that aspect of this game:  that a favor done by you can easily become a favor done to you.  I agree that the Oasis on Rathe has been good for me in that regard.  Good hunting to all my brother and sister shaman.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
